text: Svetlana Knyazeva (born 29 May 1970) is a Russian equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Russia Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nizhny Novgorod
